程序包 cn.com.hiocde

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    DFAM
    DFAM is a definite finite automata which is used for identifying token by 3-type grammar definition.
    DFAState
    DFAState inherits State , represents a DFA state.
    Item
    Item includes three keys : production , dot position , searching symbols
    ItemsCluster
    The cluster of itemsets , also include LR table and control center of phaser.
    ItemSet
    Include the set of items and map relations.
    State
    State is abstract of NFA State , including state id and map relations.
